{"tid":2204944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"轟抗疫基金3.0未向打工仔對症下藥 民主黨促全民再回水1萬元","createTime":"2020-09-16T12:03:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T12:12:22.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1d257a2ded9d50d11927fdba105f5e4c72f7d541","tid":2204944,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T12:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Uw2WtQfrNn38n4a8mhKMYtvpafE=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PXIONZNGGNEXHIHM5VB4TM6SGU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUw2WtQfrNn38n4a8mhKMYtvpafE%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPXIONZNGGNEXHIHM5VB4TM6SGU.jpg&h=13fca115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n...<br />\n該黨建議防疫基金的資助應針對中小微企、實際經營者、全民派錢一萬元、為失業人士設失業援助金，向有需要人士派9000元，為期6個月。被問到為何建議要針對資助中小微企時，胡解釋，政府口中「受疫情嚴重影響的行業」難有科學數據驗證，加上中小微企在前兩輪防疫基金有不少「漏網之魚」，未能受惠，反而部份大企業能在「疫市下有好環境」，相信中小微企較大型企業更需要政府援助。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200916/LDMNCZDLKFFQFC2EPLVSTND4IM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200916%2FLDMNCZDLKFFQFC2EPLVSTND4IM%2F&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvSHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=f0ded795\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200916%2FLDMNCZDLKFFQFC2EPLVSTND4IM%2F&h=9f11a190\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200916/LDMNCZDLKFFQFC2EPLVSTND4IM/</a>"},{"pid":"c7ad59297e7b74780f5e7bcdd0e88f8ae1300308","tid":2204944,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T12:12:22.000Z","msg":"撐民主黨了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />民建連叫派五千食屎啦"}]}